name: Molten Bursa
description: A fully-developed bursa carved from a strong Glavenus. Can't even be lightly scorched, ever.

name: Glavenus Plate
description: A sharp scale that grows near the Glavenus's tail, it has the same role -- a short blade.

name: Glavenus Fire Orb
description: A red orb that grows within a flaming bursa. One peek can set even your soul aflame.

name: Glavenus Pallium
description: A legendary Glavenus scale. Those who craft it rule the earth and seize the sky.

name: Hyper Glavenus Scale
description: Darker than normal Glavenus scales, this Hyper scale emits an ominous glow.

name: Hyper Glavenus Scale X
description: Darker than normal Glavenus scales, this Hyper scale emits a steady, ominous glow.

name: Hellblade Scale
description: A Hellblade Glavenus scale. Explodes violently if not handled with care.

name: Hellblade Scale+
description: A superior Hellblade Glavenus scale. Explodes violently if not handled with care.

name: Hellblade Shard
description: A Hellblade Glavenus scale. A thoughtless slip with it will reduce the surrounding land to rubble.

name: Hellblade Shell
description: A shell taken from a Hellblade Glavenus. Explodes violently if not handled with care.

name: Hellblade Carapace
description: A hard Hellblade Glavenus shell. Explodes violently if not handled with care.

name: Hellblade Cortex
description: A hard Hellblade Glavenus shell. Handled carelessly, it can reduce the world to eternal wasteland.

name: Hellblade Powder
description: Powder taken from a Hellblade Glavenus. Explodes violently if not handled with care.

name: Tigrex Scale
description: Scale from the incredibly violent Tigrex. Incredibly massive and sturdy.

name: Tigrex Scale+
description: A flawless Tigrex scale. Can be fastened with others to become harder than steel.

name: Tigrex Shard
description: A thick Tigrex scale. Made to withstand both the searing heat and the shivering cold.

name: Tigrex Shell
description: A hard Tigrex shell capable of repelling any impact. Extreme tenacity.

name: Tigrex Carapace
description: A material hardened by the sands of time. Sharp edges show the Tigrex's ferocity.

name: Tigrex Cortex
description: A heavy Tigrex shell. Even the terrible forces of nature cannot penetrate it.

name: Tigrex Tail
description: This flexible and strong tail can make great equipment.

name: Tigrex Lash
description: A top-grade tail from a violent Tigrex. Requires a veteran artisan's skill and experience.

name: Tigrex Claw
description: A vicious foreclaw unique to the Tigrex. Other flying wyverns do not have it.

name: Tigrex Claw+
description: A claw that time has sharpened into a horrible death sentence for prey.

name: Tigrex Hardclaw
description: A highly durable Tigrex claw. Tempered by the flesh and blood of its prey.

name: Tigrex Fang
description: A terrifying fang used to crush prey. Makes all who see it quiver in fear.

name: Tigrex Fang+
description: The sharp fang of a Tigrex. These fangs can cut any prey to shreds.

name: Tigrex Hardfang
description: A thick, large Tigrex fang that tore prey into unrecognizable pieces.

name: Tigrex Scalp
description: Part of the head of a violent Tigrex. Looks terrifying, as if it is still alive.

name: Tigrex Maw
description: The awe-inspiring jaws of a Tigrex, ready to crush both bone and spirit.

name: Tigrex Mantle
description: A phantasmal scale of a Tigrex. Those who craft it rule the earth and seize the sky.

name: Hyper Tigrex Scale
description: Darker than normal Tigrex scales, this Hyper scale emits an ominous glow.

name: Hyper Tigrex Scale X
description: Darker than normal Tigrex scales, this Hyper scale emits a steady, ominous glow.

name: Grimclaw Scale
description: A Grimclaw Tigrex scale. Dark and thickly layered. Features exceptional hardness.

name: Grimclaw Scale+
description: A superior Grimclaw Tigrex scale. A scale of the highest quality.

name: Grimclaw Shard
description: A scale from a Grimclaw Tigrex. Even the dark inner layers are exceptionally hard.

name: Grimclaw Shell
description: A Grimclaw Tigrex shell. You can see the thick blue blood vessels pulsating on its exterior.

name: Grimclaw Carapace
description: You can see the blue blood vessels pulsating on the exterior of the shell.

name: Grimclaw Cortex
description: You can see the blue blood vessels pulsating violently on the shell's exterior.

name: Grimclaw Talon
description: A talon from a Grimclaw Tigrex. It's as frightening and deadly as it looks.

name: Grimclaw Talon+
description: A quality talon from a Grimclaw Tigrex. It's as frightening and deadly as it looks.

name: Grimclaw Hardclaw
description: This high-quality Grimclaw Tigrex claw is the embodiment of ferocity.

name: Seregios Bladescale
description: A dangerous scale that opens at the tip to viscerally attack the beast's foes.

name: Seregios Slavescale
description: A sharp scale the Seregios can make stand on end. Gouges anything it touches.

name: Seregios Slavescale+
description: A sharp scale that stands on end as its master angers and rips prey to awful pieces.

name: Airblade Shard
description: A fragment from a Seregios's Airblade. Despite its small size, it shouldn't be underestimated.

name: Seregios Airblade
description: A blade shot from the body and carried on the wind toward unsuspecting hunters.

name: Seregios Airblade+
description: One of a seemingly limitless supply of wild blades shot at any who dare approach.

name: Seregios Talon
description: The hard and sharp talon of a Seregios. It is capable of tearing most armor to shreds.

name: Seregios Carver
description: Hooked hind leg talons that tear through armor and flesh without mercy.

name: Seregios Carver+
description: Hooked talons that strike like lightning, sharp enough to rend the very air.

name: Seregios Impaler
description: A spear-like tail covered in blade-like scales. Capable of truly horrific things.

name: Seregios Impaler+
description: A spear-like tail so hard and sharp, it passes through prey as if they were air.

name: Seregios Sunderer
description: The horn from a Seregios. Sturdy yet agile as a blade, it is perfect for crafting them.

name: Seregios Breacher
description: A sharp horn like a hefty axe that, not surprisingly, makes for fine equipment.

name: Seregios Breacher+
description: A sharp, robust horn with ripples as lovely as those in the most famed blades.

name: Seregios Wingtalon
description: A talon that grows on the wing of a Seregios. Enables superior flight and handling capabilities.

name: Seregios Scraper
description: A wing talon. Most attacks come from the hind legs; the wings serve to shift weight.

name: Seregios Scraper+
description: A sharp wing talon. This fine specimen is as good a material as a hindleg claw.

name: Seregios Dissenter
description: A single scale that points defiantly in a different direction from its brethren.

name: Seregios Lens
description: A rare pearl formed inside the body. Said to reveal invisible truths.

name: Hyper Seregios Scale
description: Darker than normal Seregios scales, this Hyper scale emits an ominous glow.

name: Hyper Seregios Scale X
description: Darker than normal Seregios scales, this Hyper scale emits a steady, ominous glow.

name: Diablos Carapace
description: A sturdy Diablos carapace. Even harder than a normal Diablos Shell.

name: Diablos Cortex
description: The rigid cortex of a Diablos, both harder and sturdier than its carapace.

name: Diablos Ridge+
description: The hardest part of a Diablos's backplate. Very difficult to carve off.

name: Diablos Chine
description: Tough Diablos backplate, strengthened by burning sands. An ideal material for armor.

name: Twisted Horn
description: A twisted Diablos horn. Used in this region for many (less twisted) purposes.

name: Majestic Horn
description: A twisted Diablos horn in great shape. Use it to make more powerful weapons.

name: Diablos Hardhorn
description: An especially elegant Diablos horn with almost perfect shape. An extremely rare material.

name: Diablos Fang
description: A large, sturdy fang used in everything from weapons to ornaments.

name: Diablos Tailcase
description: An armored tailcase that puts iron hammers to shame. This material is a keeper.

name: Diablos Tailcase+
description: A tailcase heavy enough to bend a steel hammer. Unimaginably powerful.

name: Blos Medulla
description: A rare medulla. Difficult to remove, but of great interest to researchers.

name: Hyper Diablos Cortex
description: Darker than normal Diablos shell, this Hyper shell emits a steady, ominous glow.

name: Bloodbath Cortex
description: A Bloodbath Diablos hard outer shell. It wears the scars of previous battles with honor.

name: Bloodbath Chine
description: A Bloodbath Diablos carapace. Tempered thoroughly by the blows of brave warriors.

name: Bloodbath Grimhorn
description: A Bloodbath Diablos horn. Vile enough to recall the tragedies the beast has caused.

name: Gore Magala Scale
description: A black scale artisans fear because of the ill fortune said to surround it.

name: Gore Magala Scale+
description: A deep black scale that seems to devour surrounding light, not reflect it.

name: Gore Magala Shard
description: A quality scale whose jet black, lusterless surface bewitches unwary beholders.

name: Gore Magala Shell
description: The Gore Magala's outer shell, said to eat the flesh of half-hearted attackers.

name: Gore Magala Carapace
description: The Gore Magala's handsome black suit of armor, said to negate all blows.

name: Gore Magala Cortex
description: A heavy, dark carapace which offers solid equipment, but no guarantees of sanity.

name: Gore Magala Wing
description: A writhing, jet black flight organ almost too hideous to be called a "wing."

name: Gore Magala Wing+
description: A horrifying wing that casts a hungry shadow over prey and drives them insane.

name: Gore Magala Eclipse
description: Calamitous wings that go unseen in the night, sowing disease and reaping death.

name: Antinomic Wing
description: A strange harmony between darkness and rainbow light peeking between the bones.

name: Gore Magala Ripclaw
description: A menacing claw that carves beautiful, indelible curves through soft, pink flesh.

name: Gore Magala Ripclaw+
description: A claw from a third foreleg that inflicts Frenzy and generations of suffering.

name: Gore Magala Shredder
description: A grotesque claw that sows madness. Some Smithies shun it, fearing infection.

name: Gore Magala Tail
description: A pliant tail covered in reverse scales that strikes like a whip, not a blade.

name: Gore Magala Lash
description: A black tail covered in sharp inverted scales that shred prey at a stroke.

name: Gore Magala Plate
description: Plating from the wing-limbs of the Gore Magala. Hunger and madness deepen the hue.

name: Contrary Scale
description: A scale with a mix of white and black that seem to be trying to devour each other.

name: Gore Magala Nyctgem
description: A pure, dark jewel that imprisons and then destroys all nearby light.

name: Gore Magala Mantle
description: A scale considered unfind- able. Equipment made with it yields superhuman power.

name: Gore Magala Feeler
description: The Gore Magala's versatile sensory organ and lifeline. It serves many purposes.

name: Gore Magala Feeler+
description: A well-honed sensory organ that oozes violet melancholy from its infected tip.

name: Gore Magala Sensor
description: A large horn that pulses purple -- an ill omen that made this a forbidden spoil.

name: Diametrical Horn
description: A sensory organ full of golden fibers that squeaks eerily as it hardens.

name: Defiled Scale
description: A Frenzy-infested scale with patches of sickly color that make for a dangerous weapon.

name: Chaos Scale
description: A shape-shifting scale whose jet-black cornified layer has turned a golden white.

name: Hyper G.Magala Scale
description: Darker than normal Gore Magala scales, this Hyper scale emits an ominous glow.

name: Hyper G.Magala Scale X
description: Darker than normal Gore Magala scales, this Hyper scale emits a steady, ominous glow.

name: S.Magala Scale
description: A shining scale just shy of blinding white. Dignified, like an ancient dragon.

name: S.Magala Scale+
description: A golden-white scale whose light stays with the eye through a thousand nights.

name: S.Magala Shard
description: An especially thick, white scale. Fully matured, it boasts wall-like resistance.

name: S.Magala Shell
description: A layered shell from which scratches seem to disappear before one's very eyes.

name: S.Magala Carapace
description: Celestial armor the Shagaru Magala once wore: an impervious font of light.

name: S.Magala Cortex
description: Impregnable armor. It is said humankind possesses no means of breaching it.

name: S.Magala Prismwing
description: A newly grown wing whose seemingly airy membranes belie rock-like strength.

name: S.Magala Prismwing+
description: A wing that casts iridescent light in the sun. Thinner wings sell at higher prices.

name: S.Magala Lightwing
description: A divine wing that guides the living toward both prosperity and ruin.

name: S.Magala Caress
description: A claw with a mystic shimmer that hardens with age. Used like a tree's growth rings.

name: S.Magala Caress+
description: A tender claw that hardens only in the face of danger, then kills softly.

name: S.Magala Purifier
description: A Shagaru Magala claw in its hardest form. Proof of the beast's death and rebirth.

name: S.Magala Tail
description: A white tail whose sheer muscularity is concealed by a coat of bristly scales.

name: S.Magala Lash
description: A strong tail with inverted scales. Its pure white color is proof of its fine quality.

name: S.Magala Plate
description: A back scale claimed only by hunters who stand beneath the beast's wings and survive.

name: S.Magala Phosgem
description: A pure jewel of light that ignites the skies and eradicates all darkness.

name: S.Magala Mantle
description: A white scale believed lost. It can be used to create gear with superhuman power.

name: S.Magala Horn
description: A hardened sensory organ. The Frenzy's madness is still locked inside.

name: S.Magala Horn+
description: A heroic arch whose hues have been changed; even now the Frenzy pollutes it.

name: S.Magala Hardhorn
description: A Shagaru Magala horn. These are said to withstand the test of time and never decay.

name: Pure Scale
description: A scale of forbidden white whose complete lack of impurities is truly rare.

name: Rajang Horn+
description: The majestic golden horn of a Rajang. Hunters yearn for the heroism it represents.

name: Rajang Hardhorn
description: A large, majestic golden horn. All who see it feel the over- whelming bravery of its owner.

name: Rajang Fang+
description: This sharpened fang can cut through anything dumb enough to touch it.

name: Rajang Hardfang
description: A Rajang fang that cuts through anything. A prey's life vanishes in an instant once caught.

name: Rajang Blackfur
description: Black Rajang fur. When crafted, the resulting fabric is desired even by royalty.

name: Rajang Wildpelt
description: A wild set of fur from a Rajang. When forged, the jet-black fur causes the wearer to rage.

name: Rajang Claw+
description: A sharp Rajang claw. Difficult to carve and more difficult to craft.

name: Rajang Hardclaw
description: A hard Rajang claw that's taken a multitude of lives in a manner best left unsaid.

name: Rajang Tail
description: The glistening tail of a Rajang. The golden fur is beautiful and elegant.

name: Gold Rajang Pelt
description: Fur taken from a Rajang's body. The golden hair is treasured by tailors.

name: Gold Rajang Pelt+
description: A golden pelt that shimmers with the same furious power as a Rajang.

name: Rajang Ragehair
description: Hair that hardens when a Rajang becomes furious. Armorsmiths line up for it.

name: Rajang Apoplexy
description: A long mane which still bristles with rage. The hairs are fine, but robust.

name: Rajang Nerve
description: The source of a Rajang's power, which continues its mystic pulsing after death.

name: Rajang Heart
description: A symbol of flesh-searing rage that releases massive power with every beat.

name: Ghoulish Gold Horn
description: The golden horn of a furious Rajang. It seems almost too lovely to waste on equipment.

name: Ghoulish Gold Gorer
description: A golden horn that seethes with rage even now. Not to be touched with bare hands.

name: Hyper Rajang Fur
description: Darker than normal Rajang fur, this Hyper scale emits an ominous glow.

name: Hyper Rajang Fur X
description: Darker than normal Rajang fur, this Hyper fur emits a steady, ominous glow.

name: Deviljho Scale
description: A greenish-black Deviljho scale. It's not often sold, as rumors claim it brings misfortune.

name: Deviljho Shard
description: A heavy, high-quality Deviljho scale. Rumored to be bad luck, but is excellent material.

name: Deviljho Crook
description: An unsettling scale that became warped as it absorbed the hate of the Deviljho's various prey.

name: Deviljho Hide
description: Black hide that is oddly slimy and difficult to forge with.

name: Deviljho Blackpiel
description: Thick hide taken from a violent Deviljho. Especially slimy and difficult to forge with.

name: Bloodied Ebonhide
description: A hide bloodied and battered from ceaseless hunts that give it no time to dry.

name: Deviljho Tallfang
description: A large fang from a maw of alarming size. Helps the vile beast sate its hunger.

name: Deviljho Hardfang
description: A massive fang that tears, crushes, and grinds prey without mercy.

name: Vile Fang
description: A massive, overgrown fang that can chomp through anything. Filled with pure evil.

name: Deviljho Talon
description: A dangerously sharp, hooked talon. Inexperienced crafters risk serious injury.

name: Deviljho Ripper
description: An incredibly sharp, rigid talon. Even experienced handlers can be injured if not careful.

name: Deviljho Scalp
description: Removing this part of a Deviljho's skull releases an unimaginably putrid odor.

name: Deviljho Tail
description: A massive tail resembling a giant leech. Some folks are out to collect these exclusively.

name: Deviljho Flail
description: A large slab of a Deviljho's leech-like tail. Even so-called experts are shocked by it.

name: Deviljho Saliva
description: The symbol of a Deviljho's insatiable appetite. The strong acid corrodes all it touches.

name: Black Blood
description: Dark black blood characteristic of a Deviljho. It feels like it may jump up and attack at any time.

name: Spattered Hide
description: A jet black hide with a slimy, tar-like sheen: dried blood spatter, some insist.

name: Deviljho Gem
description: A precious gem said to contain a Deviljho's might. Used in shady rituals.

name: Hyper Deviljho Scale
description: Darker than normal Deviljho scales, this Hyper scale emits an ominous glow.

name: Hyper Deviljho Scale X
description: Darker than normal Deviljho scales, this Hyper scale emits a steady, ominous glow.

name: Kirin Thunderhorn
description: The horn of Kirin, as powerful as a lightning bolt. Exquisite material.

name: Kirin Hide
description: A rare and lovely hide, but difficult to carve loose and dangerous to handle.

name: Kirin Hide+
description: A rare and lovely hide. This one is undamaged: proof of its former owner's strength.

name: Kirin Finehide
description: Beautiful Kirin hide that hunters can only fantasize of obtaining.

name: Kirin Mane
description: A rare, dashing mane that retains its dignity even after being cut free.

name: Platinum Mane
description: Kirin mane that sparkles like platinum. It shimmers when kissed by the wind. Priceless.

name: Kirin Thundertail
description: A rare tail, overflowing with elegance, charged with electricity.

name: Kirin Thunderlash
description: The highly rare tail of Kirin. The electricity stored within causes it to glimmer.

name: Kirin Azure Horn
description: An azure horn, rare even among Kirin Horns. Gives off a divine light.

name: Kirin Azure Peak
description: A dangerous horn containing the charge of the thousand bolts that struck it.

name: Daora Shell
description: The shining silver Kushala Daora shell is solid and highly useful.

name: Daora Carapace
description: A shell hardened by time. Crafting it is incredibly difficult.

name: Daora Cortex
description: The repeated molting of skin has made this shell near impregnable.

name: Daora Scale
description: A scale that glows a dull silver. Hard enough to serve as an abrasive for weapons.

name: Daora Dragon Scale+
description: High-quality scale from Kushala Daora. It is said to surpass steel.

name: Daora Shard
description: A thick scale from Kushala Daora. The winters have made it strong and cold to the touch.

name: Daora Webbing
description: Hard to craft but highly compatible with metals. Valued for its light weight.

name: Daora Fellwing
description: A curious wing that's strong as steel, but soft to the touch. Highly sought after material.

name: Daora Horn
description: The gallant horn of Daora. Using it requires extra- ordinary experience.

name: Daora Hardhorn
description: A hard, ferocious horn that engulfs everything in a freezing wind on impact.

name: Daora Horn+
description: A fierce-looking horn that instantly robs the body of cold if handled improperly.

name: Daora Tail
description: Cut from Kushala Daora. Incredibly destructive power contained within.

name: Daora Lash
description: The durable tail of Kushala Daora. As strong as any storm, but flexible as well.

name: Daora Claw
description: Kushala Daora's claw. As hard as ore, it cannot be used by ordinary crafters.

name: Daora Claw+
description: Even now the black gleam of this claw seems to emit a life force.

name: Daora Hardclaw
description: A robust claw one might mistake for steel. Enhances equipment capabilities.

name: Daora Gem
description: A rare gem formed inside a Daora. Its glow is breathtaking.

name: Lrg Elder Dragon Gem
description: A giant, ultra-rare stone that forms inside an Elder Dragon once in a millennium.

name: Chameleos Hide
description: This hide is so strange to the touch, you'll want to rub it all over your face.

name: Chameleos Hide+
description: Superior hide of Chameleos. Strange to the touch, but very durable.

name: Chameleos Finehide
description: Top-grade Chameleos hide. Its strange texture calms the soul of those who touch it.

name: Chameleos Horn
description: Faintly glows with a white light. Great for interior decorating.

name: Chameleos Spike
description: A sharp horn of a Chameleos. Strong and hard, but strangely easy to work with.

name: Chameleos Hardhorn
description: A super-hard horn that refracts light. A highly sought commodity.

name: Chameleos Claw
description: Thin, yet incredibly strong and very easy to work with during crafting.

name: Chameleos Claw+
description: Sharpened claw of a Chameleos. Small and sharp, but still valued for being easy to work with.

name: Chameleos Hardclaw
description: A tough Chameleos claw. Its slender sharpness and strength make it an exceptional weapon.

name: Chameleos Webbing
description: Thin, light wing webbing. The inner part of the webbing is highly durable.

name: Chameleos Fellwing
description: A top-grade Chameleos wing. The strong, firm frame makes it invaluable as material.

name: Chameleos Tail
description: The distinctive tail of Chameleos. Feels very strange.

name: Chameleos Lash
description: The tough, hard tail of Chameleos. The unique texture makes for excellent material.

name: Chameleos Gem
description: A rare gem formed inside Chameleos. It has a multi-colored glow.

name: Teostra Shell
description: The red hot shell of Teostra. It proves its domain over all fire.

name: Teostra Carapace
description: Harder than Teostra Shell. Looks like red-hot steel; particularly eye catching.

name: Teostra Cortex
description: Merely looking upon this heavy shell is enough to shatter the hearts of hardened warriors.

name: Teostra Mane
description: This majestic mane is a sure sign of Teostra's regality.

name: Teostra Tail
description: Covered in red scales, the tree like tail of Teostra is incredibly hard to cut.

name: Teostra Lash
description: The stone-hard tail of Teostra. A lash from this tail unleashes unimaginable explosions.

name: Teostra Horn
description: A horn that displays the power of Teostra. Hunters wither before its might.

name: Teostra Horn+
description: A sharp horn that burns with the fury of Teostra. It is tinged with fire.

name: Teostra Hardhorn
description: A majestic horn that commands all who gaze upon it to bend the knee.

name: Fire Dragon Scale
description: A scalding hot scale. It'll take your fingerprints right off.

name: Fire Dragon Scale+
description: A scale from a majestic fire dragon. It burns with hot fire from within.

name: Flame Shard
description: The highest quality scale from Teostra. Hunters can only dream of finding one.

name: Fire Dragon Claw
description: A sharp, glowing Fire Dragon claw. Hard even for experts to craft.

name: Teostra Claw+
description: A death sentence to he who tries to elude the dragon's flames. Still feels hot.

name: Fire Dragon Hardclaw
description: A hard, fiery Teostra claw. It causes anything it scratches to burst into flames.

name: Teostra Webbing
description: Wing webbing carved from a fire dragon. A marvelous material with many uses.

name: Teostra Powder
description: Powder from fire dragon wings. Said to magnify a material's abilities.

name: Teostra Gem
description: A rare gem formed inside a fire dragon. Flickers with ferocious flames.

name: Wyvern Crystal
description: A mysterious crystal that glows with the energy of both light and dark spirits.

name: Great Wyvern Crystal
description: A mysterious crystal of light and dark spirits. The owner is said to gain godlike powers.

name: Akantor Scale+
description: Faintly glittering Akantor Scale. It will not melt, even if dipped in lava.

name: Akantor Shard
description: A splendid scale with a faint glow. Requires cooling after all that time in lava.

name: Akantor Carapace
description: Shining Akantor Shell. Exceptionally hard, and thus difficult to craft.

name: Akantor Cortex
description: Bulky plating with a faint glow. Deters most attacks and repels the rest.

name: Akantor Tail
description: The large rock-like tail of an Akantor. Strong enough to gouge the earth.

name: Akantor Flail
description: A barbed tail that razes the earth and knocks the fight right out of prey.

name: Akantor Hardclaw
description: Hard Akantor claw that can smash bedrock. Its victims are left unrecognizable.

name: Akantor Shredtalon
description: An earth-shredding claw that destroys anything caught in the Akantor's charge.

name: Akantor Tallfang
description: Huge fang that can pierce the heavens. It has passed through many foes.

name: Akantor Greatfang
description: One of a pair of towering fangs. The hard base makes it ideal equipment material.

name: Akantor Spike
description: A flawless spike from an Akantor. It can easily scar rock.

name: Akantor Thickspike
description: A thick, sturdy shell spike believed to have evolved as defense against larger foes.

name: Akantor Gem
description: A gem that once belonged to the Ancient World-King. Its aura resists new ownership.

name: Conquest Sphere
description: A gem said to grant dominion over everything under the sun. Courses with ambition.

name: Ukanlos Carapace
description: The minerals encrusted in this cold-infused shell make it surprisingly strong.

name: Ukanlos Cortex
description: The minerals encrusted in this cold-infused cortex make it surprisingly strong.

name: Ukanlos Underscale
description: A thick, sharp belly scale. Cuts through snow, allowing Ukanlos to move easier.

name: Ukanlos Underscale+
description: A thick, sharp belly scale. Used to get around by cutting through the ice.

name: Ukanlos Tail
description: The icy tail of Ukanlos. A single lash makes the air scream and the earth cry.

name: Ukanlos Flail
description: A giant, icy Ukanlos tail. One swipe makes the air scream and glaciers crack.

name: Ukanlos Digger
description: An Ukanlos claw. Repeated voyages through the ice have twisted its shape.

name: Ukanlos Digger+
description: An impossibly massive claw with ridges used to pull the monster onto the ice.

name: Ukanlos Shoveljaw
description: Ukanlos's shovel-like jaw. Developed to shovel snow, one scoop can cause an avalanche.

name: Ukanlos Shoveljaw+
description: A prominent jaw that makes for a real spectacle when it smashes apart hunks of ice.

name: Ukanlos Fin+
description: A huge dorsal fin with saw-like ridges at the tip that cut through anything.

name: Ukanlos Strongfin
description: A giant, saw-like fin that runs along the Ukanlos's back. Cuts through all.

name: Ukanlos Gem
description: A gem owned by a king who nearly ended the world. It seeks to destroy new owners.

name: Ukanlos Stone
description: A legendary Ukanlos stone. Those who craft it rule the earth and seize the sky.

name: Alatreon Scute
description: A unique plating that can protect against attacks, and even deflect blows.

name: Alatreon Pallium
description: A miraculous plate impervious to all attacks. Legend says the bearer receives heaven's love.

name: Alatreon Plate
description: This particular Alatreon scale grows in backwards. It is as sharp as a blade.

name: Alatreon Mantle
description: The mantle of Alatreon is the stuff of legend, containing traces of every element within.

name: Alatreon Talon
description: A talon capable of making weapons of untold power. Ridiculously sharp.

name: Alatreon Riptalon
description: The mere sight of this deadly talon calls forth images of terrible weapons made from it.

name: Alatreon Webbing
description: At times this looks like a dark abyss; at others, like the coming of first light.

name: Alatreo Direwing
description: This vile wing can cut through time and space to destroy the entire world...say the rumors.

name: Alatreon Tail
description: The tail from an Alatreon, previously thought to only have existed in legend.

name: Alatreo Diretail
description: "Is this a dream?" "Am I alive?" Those who grasp this tail begin to harbor such doubts.

name: Broken Skypiercer
description: A piece of the horn from atop an Alatreon's head. Broken due to the difficulty harvesting it.

name: Skypiercer
description: Part of an Alatreon's convoluted horns.

name: Skyswayer
description: Part of an Alatreon's convoluted horns. The finest specimen known to exist.

name: Azure Dragongem
description: The legend to beat all legends. It is said to bring about the end of those who obtain it.

name: Azure Dragonsphire
description: Legend says the discovery of this brilliant gem heralds the end of the world.

name: Amatsu Carapace
description: Black armor beaten by fierce winds into powerful defense for a celestial god.

name: Amatsu Cortex
description: This black armor, forged by the storm for a malevolent god, is almost unmatched in strength.

name: Amatsu Webbing
description: Ethereal robes that make one appear to float, like something out of a fable.

name: Amatsu Membrane
description: Legendary material that, when worn, can even allow the wearer to float for a short time.

name: Amatsu Horn
description: A horn carved from an Amatsu. The unblemished horns are proof of its strength.

name: Amatsu Hardhorn
description: A horn carved from an Amatsu. It was grown in the midst of ferocious storms.

name: Amatsu Claw+
description: The incredibly sharp claw of an Amatsu. Just seeing the claw will instill fear of its owner.

name: Amatsu Hardclaw
description: The incredibly sharp claw of an Amatsu. Just seeing the claw inspires intense fear.

name: Amatsu Tail
description: The tail of the Storm Dragon. It is very tough, which helps maneuverability in the storm.

name: Amatsu Stormtail
description: The gorgeous tail of the Storm Dragon. Its dancing movements are said to call the storm.

name: Amatsu Pleura
description: A chestplate that is said to steal the future of those who bathe in its passionate light.

name: Amatsu Heavypleura
description: A heavy chestplate whose light emits despair. The passion it inspires is particularly strong.

name: Storm Vesicle
description: Unique organ that stores large amounts of water. Even a sliver can power up your gear.

name: Storm Vesicle Clump
description: A particularly well-developed organ that stores enough water to wash away the world.

name: Heavenly Dragongem
description: The root of the celestial gods' power. It grants their far-reaching vision.

name: Heavenly Dragonsphire
description: The root of the celestial gods' power. It grants their far-reaching vision.

name: Dragon Healing Crystal
description: A hard crystal made from dragon scales. Valued as medicine. (Account Item)

name: Lao-Shan Shard
description: The thick scale of Lao-Shan. Its hardness is on par with any wyvern cortex.

name: Lao-Shan Cortex
description: An unbelievably heavy shell from Lao-Shan. The ages have made this shell immortal.

name: Lao-Shan Hardhorn
description: Horn from a Lao-Shan Lung snout. Perfectly formed even without forging -- a true luxury item.

name: Lao-Shan Megaclaw
description: A Lao-Shan Lung claw. So gigantic that even skilled artisans find themselves unable to work it.

name: Lao-Shan Mantle
description: A legendary scale of Lao-Shan. Those who craft it rule the earth and seize the sky.

name: Fatalis Shard
description: A thick, jet-black scale that covers the body of Fatalis. Grows thick with age.

name: Fatalis Cortex
description: Harder than a Fatalis shell, it's also known as Mediastinum.

name: Fatalis Hardhorn
description: A horn of immense strength. The black glow of the horn gives off a strange attraction.

name: Fatalis Evil Eye
description: An unusual aura surrounds the eye of Fatalis. Perhaps it's possessed...

name: Fatalis Fellwing
description: A wing hard as any metal, yet still very malleable. Only the most skilled can work with it.

name: Crimson Fatalis Scale
description: The scale of a Fatalis overcome with rage. Crimson fire hides a deep darkness.

name: Crimson Fatalis Shell
description: The shell of a Fatalis overcome with rage. It shines an unforgiving crimson.

name: Crimson Fatalis Horn
description: The horn of a Fatalis overcome with rage. It looks ready to tear down the sky.

name: Crimson Fatalis Wing
description: The wing of a Fatalis overcome with rage. The air fears its crimson pulse.

name: Fatalis Devileye+
description: The eye of a Fatalis overcome with rage. Its wicked gaze devours one's courage.

name: Old Fatalis Shard
description: A sparkling white scale of an ancient Fatalis. Its beauty can capture your heart.

name: Old Fatalis Cortex
description: A sparkling white shell of an ancient Fatalis. Heavier and stronger than most parts.

name: Old Fatalis Hardhorn
description: A sparkling white horn of an ancient Fatalis. Said to be lightning personified.

name: Old Fatalis Fellwing
description: A sparkling white wing of an ancient Fatalis. To gaze upon it is to know true oppression.

name: Old Fatalis Souleye
description: A crimson eye, fierce and unforgiving, that gazes back with red, electric finality.

name: Nakarkos Husk
description: The outer shell covering the Nakarkos. Used for crafting, but not much else is known.

name: Nakarkos Husk+
description: Bones that have become hardened somehow due to the fluid of a Nakarkos.

name: Heavy Nakarkos Husk
description: These bones have become impossibly hard after years of soaking in Nakarkos fluid.

name: Nakarkos Shell
description: The outer shell covering the Nakarkos. Its properties make for great armor.

name: Nakarkos Shell+
description: A spiny outer shell, it has undergone many changes over time, making it quite unique.

name: Nakarkos Hardshell
description: The outer shell covering the Nakarkos. Its hardness makes truly top-class armor.

name: Nakarkos Skull
description: A horrifying skull that strikes fear into the hearts of all who see it.

name: Nakarkos Hardskull
description: A hair-raisingly frightening skull. Said to induce fainting in those who gaze upon its horror.

name: Nakarkos Vertebra
description: The sound of this bone terrifies all who hear it. Surprisingly easy to work with.

name: Nakarkos Hardvertebra
description: The echoing sound of this bone brings madness to all who hear it. Valuable and easy to work with.

name: Nakarkos Hide
description: The beautiful blue hide of a Nakarkos. It is hard to tear despite its elasticity.

name: Nakarkos Azurehide
description: The beautiful blue hide of a Nakarkos. Both incredibly strong and highly-prized.

name: Nakarkos Arm Brace
description: A keratinized brace from the oral arm of a Nakarkos. Hard and oozing a strong adhesive.

name: Scary Nakarkos ArmBrce
description: A keratinized brace from the oral arm of a Nakarkos. Stickier and harder than ever.

name: Nakarkos Fang
description: One of countless fangs in the mouth of a Nakarkos. It can crunch through bone with ease.

name: Nakarkos Cuttlebone
description: A small white bone that is found inside the body of a Nakarkos.

name: Lrg Nakarkos Cuttlebone
description: A huge white bone found inside the body of a Nakarkos. Though called a bone, it's more of a shell.

name: Nakarkos Soul Orb
description: A jewel formed in a Nakarkos from the remains of the endless prey it has devoured.

name: Nakarkos SecretSoulOrb
description: An extremely rare jewel formed inside a Narkakos from the remains of its prey.

name: Radiant Mucus
description: A viscous liquid produced by the Nakarkos. It gives off an ominous glow.

name: Radiant Mucus+
description: Nakarkos mucus is said to help prevent the deterioration of bone materials.

name: Viscous Radiant Mucus
description: Good quality Narkakos mucus. Keeps bone in good condition and can harden it too.

name: Valstrax Scale+
description: A high-quality Valstrax scale that can withstand movement at the speed of sound.

name: Valstrax Shard
description: A faintly glittering silver Valstrax scale. Precious dragon scales like these were once used in rituals.

name: Valstrax Carapace
description: A sturdy Valstrax outer shell. Not even impacts at the speed of sound can mar it.

name: Valstrax Cortex
description: A particularly hard shell inside Valstrax's outer shell. Light and strong, it's of the finest quality.

name: Valstrax Claw+
description: This piece of Valstrax claw is remarkably hard and sharp. It's torn up countless peacetimes.

name: Valstrax Hardclaw
description: A fierce-looking Valstrax claw. Just the sight of this disaster- bringing claw chills the blood.

name: Valstrax Tail
description: A large Valstrax tail that shines like a comet. Effortlessly sweeps aside all tranquility.

name: Valstrax Helixtail
description: A beautifully sharp section of Valstrax tail. Glows eerily like the tail of a comet.

name: Valstrax Lancewing
description: A Valstrax wing, capable of infinite subtle variety. Requires special handling to work with.

name: Valstrax Lancewing+
description: A rare piece of Valstrax wing, the pointed tip changes shape and is used to attack prey.

name: Valstrax Spineshell
description: A Valstrax shell used to protect its back. Its sharp, glittering points look like sharpened blades.

name: Valstrax Spineshell+
description: A very rare piece of spine- protecting Valstrax shell that gleams like a giant mirror.

name: Red Dragon Mindstone
description: The source of evil heavenly omens. The owner gains the power of the red comet.

name: Ruby Dragon Mindstone
description: The source of evil heavenly omens. The owner gains the power to bring disaster.

name: Burned Husk
description: An object that dropped from a comet, of great interest to the Wycademy researchers.

name: Shimmering Dragonfluid
description: The red light this Valstrax fluid emits is always slightly warm.

name: Golden Silk
description: Golden thread left behind by an Ahtal-Ka. Its tensile strength and great beauty give it value.

name: Ahtal-Ka Gold Cocoon
description: A shimmering golden Ahtal-Ka shell. Its ancient surface is filled with mysterious beauty.

name: Ahtal-Ka Purple Cocoon
description: A purple piece of Ahtal-Ka shell. Worth much more than the ordinary shells.

name: Ahtal-Ka Foreblade
description: A piece of sharp Ahtal-Ka foreleg. Note its fantastic cutting ability and attractive glitter.

name: Iridescent Carapace
description: A piece of Ahtal-Ka shell. Its color changes depending on the angle of the light.

name: Ahtal-Ka Pheromone
description: A fragrant liquid secreted by an Ahtal-Ka. Its scent is so strong it can be detected for miles.

name: Ahtal-Ka Fine Silk
description: A bright thread spun by an Ahtal-Ka. Contains beautiful crystalline patterns.

name: Ahtal-Ka Alluring Gem
description: A jewel that will bewitch a beholder forever. Created after an eternity deep in the ruins.

name: Royal Pyroxene
description: The pyroxene throne created such fear among the people that they could only kneel before it.

name: Map
description: A complete field map that shows terrain. (Supply Item)

name: First-aid Med
description: Restores a small amount of Health. (Supply Item)

name: First-aid Med+
description: Restores a moderate amount of Health. (Supply Item)

name: Ration
description: Restores a small amount of Stamina. (Supply Item)

name: Portable Spit
description: A portable spit issued to new hunters. Get cookin'! (Supply Item)

name: Mini Whetstone
description: A portable Whetstone for restoring Sharpness to weapons. (Supply Item)

name: EZ Shock Trap
description: Immobilizes a target for easy capture. (Supply Item)

name: EZ Flash Bomb
description: A grenade-like bomb that flashes brightly on impact. (Supply Item)

name: EZ Sonic Bomb
description: A grenade-like bomb that emits a loud, high-frequency sound. (Supply Item)

name: EZ Max Potion
description: Fully restores Health and maximizes your Health Gauge. (Supply Item)

name: EZ Lifepowder
description: Heals those within range with a single touch. (Supply Item)

name: EZ Dust of Life
description: Disperses on use and heals serious injuries instantly. (Supply Item)

name: EZ Pitfall Trap
description: Activates a pitfall to catch monsters with. (Supply Item)

name: EZ Barrel Bomb L
description: A powered-up Barrel Bomb L. Just as potent as a Barrel Bomb L+. (Supply Item)

name: EZ Hunter's Drink
description: Temporarily makes it easier to refill the Hunter Arts Gauge. (Supply Item)

name: Ballista Ammo
description: Ammunition for the large Ballista. (Supply Item)

name: One-shot Binder
description: Ballista ammo that restrains targets. Disposable ammo, no cooldown. (Supply Item)

name: Anti-dragon Bomb
description: A small time bomb that can be stuck directly on targets you mount. (Supply Item)

name: Dense Marcoal
description: Special fuel used with the Demolisher. Requires a cooldown between uses. (Supply Item)

name: Paw Pass Ticket
description: Deliver to end the Quest. Maybe the Felynes will take you home... (Supply Item)

name: EZ Farcaster
description: Instantly transports you back to base camp. (Supply Item)

name: Rusted Fragment
description: An oddly shaped metal fragment covered in rust. It looks like it could be used for something...

name: Ancient Fragment
description: A metal fragment taken from deep in the earth. Still strong, and maybe useful...

name: Mythical Fragment
description: An unidentifiably old piece of metal that gives off a mystical light. Might be usable somehow.

name: Sinister Cloth
description: Found long ago in the tomb of a king from a long forgotten desert land.

name: Sinister Darkcloth
description: A burial cloth said to have been used on the ancient king in the desert. Believed to be cursed.

name: Sinister Gloomcloth
description: A cloth worn by a messenger of a far away, long ago underworld. Can supposedly absorb life.

name: Extravagant Artifact
description: Either the burial item of an ancient dynasty, or a cache of pirate treasure. How exciting!

name: Opulent Artifact
description: Some people spend their entire lives looking for this kind of haul.

name: Decadent Artifact
description: To gaze upon this dazzling ornament is to gaze upon a star, and have your heart stolen away.

name: Broken Statue
description: An ancient-looking statue. Bears no hints as to when and why it was made, or by whom.

name: Large Broken Statue
description: A massive statue left from an epic time. Has been exposed to the elements for eons.

name: Broken Cat God Statue
description: A solemn stone cat statue, redolent of history's riddles. A god messenger, or religious icon?

name: Dark Piece
description: A mysterious, ominous piece of Dark Stone. Crafting it is a scary proposition.

name: Dark Stone
description: A jet-black stone with an ominous aura. Holding it wraps one in despair.

name: Felyne Kettle
description: A kettle the Felyne have poured their sheer joy into. Don't forget to remove it from the heat!

name: Yukumo Riceflour
description: An ingredient for making sweets. However, it can become quite hard if prepared incorrectly.

name: Doll Parts
description: It is usually given as a gift to small children. However, if you give it to an artisan...

name: Weapon Codex
description: A secret text that describes the crafting process for a weapon from a far-off land.

name: Bowgun Codex
description: A secret text that describes the crafting process for a Bowgun from a far-off land.

name: Deluxe Barrel Timber
description: Unique wood that won't break even when bent, so the barrels it makes can be used as armor.

name: Ancient Talisman
description: A talisman enshrining the holiness of an eastern god. The Smithy might give you new insight...

name: Damaged Amber
description: This strange amber is the subject of ongoing research. It could be used in crafting.

name: Cloudy Fragment
description: This scale mingles white and black, and gives off an ominous aura. Can be used in crafting.

name: Strange Mask
description: Cha-Cha and Kayamba's strongest mask...is not this one. Can be used in crafting.

name: Sunmarge Crystal
description: A very rare crystal, seldom seen for sale. Its fishlike form is impressive.

name: Ocean Pyroxene
description: A jewel that gives off a limpid blue glow. The whole ocean seems to be contained within it.

name: Fluffy White Ball
description: A snow-white ball of fluffy material. Can make a Palico even cuter!

name: Fluffy Black Ball
description: A pitch-black ball of fluffy material. Can make a Palico even cuter!

name: Fusion Material - Head
description: Material used to combine the form of one head armor with the function of another.

name: Fusion Material - Chest
description: Material used to combine the form of one chest armor with the function of another.

name: Fusion Material - Arms
description: Material used to combine the form of one set of armguards with the function of another.

name: Fusion Material - Waist
description: Material used to combine the form of one waist armor with the function of another.

name: Fusion Material - Legs
description: Material used to combine the form of one set of leg armor with the function of another.

name: F Fusion Material - Head
description: Material used to combine the form of one Palico head armor with the function of another.

name: F Fusion Material - Chest
description: Material used to combine the form of one Palico chest armor with the function of another.

name: Voucher
description: Redeem this for a special Meal with stronger effects than usual.

name: Gourmet Voucher
description: Exchange this for a kingly Meal. Both its flavor and effects are top notch.

name: Commendation
description: A ticket awarded for a display of bravery. Collect enough and it might pay off.

name: Commendation G
description: A ticket awarded for great bravery. Collect enough and it might pay off.

name: Commendation XX
description: A ticket awarded for peerless bravery. Collect enough and it might pay off.

name: Accolade XX
description: A ticket awarded to one who brings immense hope. Collect enough and it might pay off.

name: Privilege G
description: A ticket awarded to a warrior who's challenged G-rank Quests. If you give it to the Smithy...

name: Triumph
description: Evidence of one who has overcome many trials. Gives true honor to the holder.

name: Pawprint Stamp
description: Lynian paper currency, stamped with a pawprint. The letters written on it are unfamiliar.

name: Pawprint Ticket
description: A Lynian ticket decorated with bright pawprint stamps. Received in thanks for something.

name: Bherna Ticket
description: Received for contributions to Bherna Village. If you give it to the Smithy...

name: Royal Honey
description: Top quality honey fit for a queen bee. Craved for its health benefits. (Account Item)

description: The perfect shape and aroma. Even better than a Unique Mushroom. (Account Item)

description: A Unique Mushroom made more unique by maturing its aroma and flavor. (Account Item)

description: A rare mushroom that only grows from the roots of certain plants. (Account Item)

description: A flavorful mushroom that grows in the depths of the ancient forest. (Account Item)

name: Super Sprout
description: A special sprout that grows in the mountains. Considered a delicacy. (Account Item)

name: Tropical Berry
description: A bright red strawberry from scorching climes. (Account Item)

name: Mountain Herbs
description: An herb found in the Arctic Ridge and prized for its nutritiousness. (Account Item)

name: Unique Fern
description: Found only in the Jurassic Frontier. Bitter, but also sweet. (Account Item)

name: Choice Fern
description: Perfectly shaped, exquisitely bitter. Even better than a Unique Fern. (Account Item)

name: Goldenfish
description: A rare fish made of solid gold. Sell it for a tidy sum. (Account Item)

name: Silverfish
description: A rare fish made of pure silver. Sell it for a tidy sum. (Account Item)

name: Brocadefish
description: A beautiful fish with many vivid colors. Nobles keep them as pets. (Account Item)

name: King Brocadefish
description: The name given to large and particularly beautiful Brocadefish. (Account Item)

name: Premium Sashimi
description: The ultimate fatty tuna sashimi. It melts on the tongue. (Account Item)

name: Royal Rhino
description: A beetle with a jewel-like gleam that collectors pay dearly for. (Account Item)

name: Divine Rhino
description: A sublime prize from the Altaroth collectors adore. (Account Item)

name: Silver Cricket
description: A cricket with silver wings. Chirps the soothing sounds of summer. (Account Item)

name: Gold Cricket
description: A cricket with gold wings. Chirps the soothing sounds of summer. (Account Item)

description: A pretty moth that seems to live forever. It is used in medicine. (Account Item)

name: Large Immortal Moth
description: A giant Immortal Moth. Said to be able to grant eternal life. (Account Item)

description: A faint crimson ore. Emits a flowery fragrance when rubbed. (Account Item)

name: Tomato Juice
description: Delicious and filled with nutrients, this tomato juice is good to drink for those who've lost a lot of blood.

name: Fairy Tail Mark
description: A Mage Guild mark from lands far away. Proof of friendships that stand the test of time.

name: F Pirate Coin J
description: Proof that you've completed a JUMP Quest. It depicts the image of a legendary Felyne pirate.

name: Cardboard
description: Simple cardboard material, yet it has the odd effect of sparking the imagination.

name: Uniqlo Coin
description: A Uniqlo coin designed with both form and function in mind.

name: Soulstone
description: A mysterious rock said to house the soul of a monster. This one contains Fire.

name: Crows Coin
description: A coin that proves one to be the worst of the worst. The back side has the names of noted thugs.

name: Bicycle Club Application
description: Proof that one has joined the Bicycle Club. Keep pedaling until you win Nationals!

name: Arena Ticket
description: A ticket for admission to an underground arena where warriors fight to see who's the strongest.

name: Grandpaw Coin
description: A coin from Grandpaw Danger, it can be traded for Palico gear that protects its wearer from danger.

name: CoroCoro Ticket
description: A ticket adorned with the CoroCoro dragon, who brings dreams to boys and girls.

name: Ushio Coin
description: An ancient-looking coin containing a deep-seated grudge. It is used for creating demon-slaying gear.

name: Magi Coin
description: A coin given to those Magi recognize as worthy. It is used to create weapons imbued with magical power.

name: Pluto Stardust
description: A shooting star fragment used to create Shonen Magazine's special gear.

name: Roll of Fate
description: A trump card that ensures a duel's victory. A magician is beautifully drawn on one side.

name: Pirate Ticket J
description: Proof that you've conquered a JUMP Quest. It depicts a captain and his beloved sword.

name: Famitsu Ticket
description: Authorizes you to produce a special Famitsu weapon. The word "gavas" is written on it.

name: Dengeki Ticket
description: Thanks for participating in our event! Remember to pick up Dengeki Game Magazine!

name: Uniqlo Coin S
description: A special Uniqlo coin designed with both form and function in mind.

name: Wind Waker
description: A conductor's baton with the power to control the wind. Given to a legendary hero's successor.

name: Arwing Boarding Pass
description: A boarding pass for a tour on a starship. A weapon blueprint is written on the back.

name: Super Mushroom
description: A red-capped mushroom with white spots. One bite makes you big and tough.

name: Design Pattern
description: Now you can be a fashion leader just like Isabelle and Mr. Resetti!

name: Triforce
description: Proof that the goddess saw courage in the heart of a young hero clad in green.

name: Samus Coin
description: An ancient coin given to the protectors of the galaxy. A Chozo emblem is carved on one side.

name: Goddess's Grace
description: The power of the Goddess crystallized into a jewel. Grants one eternal peace.

name: Goddess's Embrace
description: The power of the Goddess crystallized into a crown. Grants one eternal honor.

name: SF Coin
description: Given to martial artists who never miss training, this coin is proof of those seeking new challenges.

name: Red Orb
description: A magical red stone that contains the blood of demons. It makes for quite stylish Palico weapons.

name: Ceratanium
description: A strong, yet light alloy developed by the father of robotics. It is the material used by a special robot.

name: Hero's Seal
description: An item given to hunters who are passionate about their craft. A true symbol of the art of hunting.

name: Baby Journal
description: A journal charting the growth of baby monsters. It includes daily observations and thoughts.

name: Sunsnug Journal
description: A journal with cute illustrations depicting the daily life of a Felyne living in a Lynian village.

name: Fan Club Newsletter
description: A newsletter for all the passionate fan club members.

name: Fan Club Application
description: An application form to join the only club for true MH-lovers! Come join the fun!

name: Fan Club Invite
description: An invite to a fan club for ardent monster hunters ONLY! Welcome to the gang.

name: Puppet Ticket
description: A ticket stamped with the paw prints of two Felynes.

name: Great Stone
description: This stone looks normal, but it has an incredible sense of presence and exudes an ancient feel.

name: Courier's Letter
description: Neither snow nor rain nor gloom of night stays the Courier from delivering people's dreams.

name: Kaioh Certificate
description: It says "Hunting is a precious skill, a refinement of the heart."

name: WORST Coin
description: A shabby coin, but proof that you've gone toe to toe with a real monster.

name: Evidence
description: Evidence left at the scene. We can infer the appearance of the perp via deduction!

name: Salaryman Coin
description: Swap for Palico hardware to defend against enraged bosses.

name: Taisha-ryu Codex
description: A swordfighting style permitted only to those who would die for honor.

name: Famitsu Coupon
description: A ticket awarded to skilled hunters that lets you create exclusive Famitsu weapons.

name: Dengeki Ticket XX
description: Thanks for taking part in our event! We hope to see you again soon!

name: Flying Xin Mark
description: Proof of membership in the elite army unit of a man who would be general.

name: Buccaneer Ticket J
description: Proof that you've conquered a Jump Quest. It depicts a captain and his sword.

name: Magic Realm Key
description: A key to unlock both realms unknown and custom gear from the Shonen Magazine Boss.

name: Zaruba Fragment
description: A piece of a magic ring that exhausted its energy to save its friends. It still glows.

name: Turnabout Ticket
description: A pass to a heated court battle. Lets you make lawyer gear at the Palico Armory.

name: Navirou Ticket
description: Lets you create gear resembling a very unique, enigmatic-looking Felyne.

name: F Spirit Stone
description: A monster's spirit seals away the Felyne power in this strange stone.

name: Club Promotion
description: Congrats! This proves that you possess true skill. You better not slack off again!

name: JDL Badge
description: Proves that you're a member of the Junior Detective League. One truth prevails!

name: Silver Crystal
description: A piece of a crystal filled with the love of a princess for her friends.

name: Zelda Ticket
description: A Triforce fragment proving that your power has been recognized by a goddess.

name: Zelda Ticket G
description: A Triforce fragment proving that your courage has been recognized by a goddess.

name: Sealing Shield
description: A shield with five shining orbs that conceal a mysterious power, which is said to protect the world from evil.

name: Option
description: A small robot that supports Hiryu on his missions by firing beams or blocking attacks.

name: Celestial Scroll
description: A beautifully drawn scroll depicting Amaterasu, the Sun Goddess, in all her divinity.

name: Arthur's Armor
description: Knight's armor for the brave and valiant. Chivalrous straw- berry-print boxers included.

name: Zelda Ticket P
description: A Triforce fragment proving that your wisdom has been recognized by a goddess.
